Privacy Policy for Content Creator
What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
Content Creator does not collect personally identifyable information, nor does it send any information anywhere.
Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by Content Creator?
No third party has access to any Content Creator data.
What are my opt-out options?
You can delete the application.
Data Retention Policy, Managing Your Information
For any local data that is collected and stored inside the application, you can delete that from your device by deleting the application.
Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time for any reason.
Business Changes
If a change of ownership, to a third party, of Content Creator or any of it's assets occurs, you acknowledge that the third party can continue to collect data as outlined in this document.
Your Consent
By using Content Creator, you are consenting to our collecting and processing of your information as set forth in this Privacy Policy now and as amended in the future.
Limited Warranties
It is not warranted that the information provided is to be accurate, up to date, complete, or remain available. To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, we exclude all representations, warranties and conditions relating to this software and the use of this software (including, without limitation, any warranties implied by law in respect of satisfactory quality, fitness for purpose and/or the use of reasonable care and skill).
